<div class="error-wrapper">

  <div class="error">

    <picture>
        <source srcset="{{#assetRewrite}}{{assetsPath}}/img/errors/5xx.svg{{/assetRewrite}}" type="image/svg+xml">
        <img srcset="{{#assetRewrite}}{{assetsPath}}/img/errors/5xx-2x.png{{/assetRewrite}} 314w" src="{{#assetRewrite}}{{assetsPath}}/img/errors/5xx.png{{/assetRewrite}}" sizes="157px"
             alt="" class="error__icon">
    </picture>

    <h1 class="error__title">Your ORCID iD settings prevented log in</h1>

    <p>Please update the visibility settings of the name associated with your ORCID iD before trying again.</p>
    <div class="error__orcid-container">
      <div class="error__orcid">
        <h3>Step 1: Open your name's visibility settings on your ORCID iD page</h3>
        <div class="error__orcid-left">
          <p>Go to <a href="https://orcid.org/my-orcid">orcid.org/my-orcid</a> to change the visbility settings of your name by using the pencil icon.</p>

          <p>It should be in the top left corner of your ORCID iD page, next to your name.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="error__orcid-right">
          <img src="/assets/img/errors/step1.jpg" alt="Step 1" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="error__orcid">
        <h3>Step 2: Change the visibility setting</h3>
        <div class="error__orcid-left">
          <p>Change the visibility setting to “everyone” or “trusted parties” and save your changes. Locking your name will not allow you to log in to eLife.</p>

          <p>You may be asked to authorise eLife as a trusted party when you try to log in again. <a href="https://support.orcid.org/hc/en-us/articles/360006894494-Visibility-preferences">Learn more about ORCID visibility settings</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="error__orcid-right">
          <img src="/assets/img/errors/step2.jpg" alt="Step 2" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="error__orcid">
        <h3>Step 3: Return to eLife and log in again</h3>
        <div class="error__orcid-left">
          <p>Return to elifesciences.org and attempt to log in again. If your are still unable to log in please <a href="https://elifesciences.org/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="error__orcid-right">
          <img src="/assets/img/errors/step3.jpg" alt="Step 3" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{#button}}
        {{> atoms-button }}
    {{/button}}

  </div>

</div>
